comment: We want Johnny Depp back as Grindelwald, or we're done with the franchise!
commentable_entity.ask: Give Johnny Depp back his role of "Grindelwald"
commentable_entity.title: Warner Brothers: Give Johnny Depp back his role of "Grindelwald"
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp announced today that he was asked to step down from his role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Beasts 3. 

I'm petitioning to allow him to play the role. He has been wronged by his ex-wife Amber Heard, who had been abusing him all throughout their marriage.

There are "mountains of evidence" to support the claim that SHE is the abuser and not Johnny, including:

-audio recordings in which she mocks and taunts him for not fighting back; calls him "fat" and "washed-up", and actually openly admits to hitting him. 

-Multiple witness account from staff, make-up artists and actual friends of hers, disproving that she was not bruised when she claimed she was.

-Multiple CCTV camera footage probing she was not injured on the dates she claims.

-Doctor/hospital reports documenting the time Johnny was injured by her, including the tip of his finger being severed by her.

The court ruling was unjust given the sheer amount of evidence to the contrary of her claims. 

This petition is hopefully to convince Warner Bros to consider giving Mr Depp his role back in FB3. I am hoping they will agree men are also victims of domestic abuse, and women CAN be abusers. I am hoping Mr Depp will receive justice. Thanks

comment:
Johnny Depp is one of the most respected, beloved actors in the world. This is what it took to tear him down to the ground: 
1. The perjury of one PROVEN abuser & liar.
2. A story in a tabloid you wouldn’t use to line a cat box.
3. One corrupt and/or compromised judge. 
Terrifying and shameful, this is spitting in the face of true victims of violence. There are MILLIONS of us worldwide fighting for justice. Amber Heard belongs in prison. Johnny Depp deserves SO MUCH better than this.

commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp announced today that he was asked to step down from his role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Beasts 3. 

I'm petitioning to allow him to play the role. He has been wronged by his ex-wife Amber Heard, who had been abusing him all throughout their marriage.

There are "mountains of evidence" to support the claim that SHE is the abuser and not Johnny, including:

-audio recordings in which she mocks and taunts him for not fighting back; calls him "fat" and "washed-up", and actually openly admits to hitting him. 

-Multiple witness account from staff, make-up artists and actual friends of hers, disproving that she was not bruised when she claimed she was.

-Multiple CCTV camera footage probing she was not injured on the dates she claims.

-Doctor/hospital reports documenting the time Johnny was injured by her, including the tip of his finger being severed by her.

The court ruling was unjust given the sheer amount of evidence to the contrary of her claims. 

This petition is hopefully to convince Warner Bros to consider giving Mr Depp his role back in FB3. I am hoping they will agree men are also victims of domestic abuse, and women CAN be abusers. I am hoping Mr Depp will receive justice. Thanks

commentable_entity.title: Warner Brothers: Give Johnny Depp back his role of "Grindelwald"
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp announced today that he was asked to step down from his role of Grindelwald in Fantastic Beasts 3. 

I'm petitioning to allow him to play the role. He has been wronged by his ex-wife Amber Heard, who had been abusing him all throughout their marriage.

There are "mountains of evidence" to support the claim that SHE is the abuser and not Johnny, including:

-audio recordings in which she mocks and taunts him for not fighting back; calls him "fat" and "washed-up", and actually openly admits to hitting him. 

-Multiple witness account from staff, make-up artists and actual friends of hers, disproving that she was not bruised when she claimed she was.

-Multiple CCTV camera footage probing she was not injured on the dates she claims.

-Doctor/hospital reports documenting the time Johnny was injured by her, including the tip of his finger being severed by her.

The court ruling was unjust given the sheer amount of evidence to the contrary of her claims. 

This petition is hopefully to convince Warner Bros to consider giving Mr Depp his role back in FB3. I am hoping they will agree men are also victims of domestic abuse, and women CAN be abusers. I am hoping Mr Depp will receive justice. Thanks
